## 8. Performance & Scalability Review

*   **N/10 Firestore Query Loop (Optimized):** Replaced nested customer loops in CRM queries with an array-contains query on `storeIds` in `useCustomers.js`.
*   **Page Pagination:** Re-enabled startAfter cursors on store-specific views to handle data sets exceeding 1,000+ orders.

